## README File  
### Score: 8/10  

The README is informative and above average for a student project. It explains the purpose of the system and provides clear setup instructions.

### What is done well:
- Clear project description and purpose
- Defined problem statement
- Feature list is included
- Installation and usage instructions are detailed
- Technology stack is listed

### What is missing:
- Real screenshots of the system
- Architecture overview (diagram or explanation)
- Clear explanation of backend–frontend interaction
- API usage examples

